-- Legg Mason interim CEO expects permanent CEO soon
-- 
-- Fri Feb 1, 2013 8:16am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/02/01/us-leggmason-results-ceo-idUSBRE9100NX20130201

 

 BOSTON  (Reuters) - Legg Mason Inc ( LM.N ) interim Chief Executive Joseph Sullivan said investors should expect the company to name a new chief executive "in the not too distant future." 
 Speaking on a conference call with investors on Friday, Sullivan said the company's board is "nearing completion" of its search for a new CEO. (Reporting By  Ross Kerber ; Editing by Gerald E. McCormick)